    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Liolaemus (Iguania: Liolaemidae) from the hot deserts of northern Patagonia, Argentina" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305645>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305653>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305655>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305659> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305645>
    dc:description "Fig. 1.Details of Liolaemus kulinko sp. nov., holotype (MPCN-H-469) (SVL 79.93 mm, tail 112.35 mm). A, C. Dorsal and ventral views of the body. B, E–F. Lateral, ventral and dorsal views of the head. D. Ventral view of precloacal pores. Photographs: P. Chafrat." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8305645/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305653>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. A, C, E, G. Coloring patterns. Adult males of Liolaemus kulinko sp. nov. in dorsal view. B, D, F, H. Adult males of L. mapuche Abdala, 2002 in dorsal view. Photographs by I. Procheret (A, C) and C.S. Abdala (B, D–H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8305653/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305655>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Map of the distribution area of Liolaemus kulinko sp. nov. (red star), type locality of the holotype (black arrow with red star) and type locality of Liolaemus mapuche Abdala, 2002 (yellow square)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8305655/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8305659>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Morphological phylogenetic tree showing the relationships between the species of Liolaemus boulengeri group, including L. kulinko sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8305659/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

